This repository (100BeautiesLab_CreationsAI) is a non-official, non-commercial
AI training dataset repository that references the source database
"100BeautiesLab_CreationsDB" as a Git submodule.

The licence terms of the source database apply to all creative works data
included via the submodule. This repository inherits and complies with the
CC BY-NC 4.0 licence.

The auto-generated index/manifest files in ai-dataset/ are derivative works
produced solely by reading the submodule data. They carry the same licence.
